body:
you have to add line in file `nginx.conf`
```
server {
    listen 80;
    charset utf-8;
    client_max_body_size 1000M;   <-- this line
    add_header X-Frame-Options DENY;
    add_header X-Content-Type-Options nosniff;
    add_header X-XSS-Protection "1; mode=block";
```
in nginx config. rebuild nginx image and docker-compose up again
